utils
Class DynamicArray<T>

java.lang.Object
  utils.DynamicArray<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Generic object type to create the array for.
public class DynamicArray<T>
extends java.lang.Object

Creates a self-sizing array with a generic parameter. This ensures that the array can be created for multiple object types and is not restricted to just one kind of object.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Muhammad Sajawal Javaid
